               Confined Six Months
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>BROWN - <rs id="t18250519-114-verdict680" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18250519-114-verdict680" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>. Aged 23.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18250519-114-punish681" type="punishmentDescription">
