                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18250519-114-defend642 t18250519-114-punish681"></join>
               Confined One Year
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>NEWELL - <rs id="t18250519-114-verdict682" type="verdictDescription">
